54066::$$$message_0470_0000_0000$$$::"Because he was on guard for my counterattack?"::
54067::$$$message_0470_0001_0000$$$::"I'm not so sure about that. From what you told me, you couldn't hurt him. And if I was Zouken, I wouldn't leave a trapped enemy any room to fight back.[lr]::
54068::$$$message_0470_0001_0001$$$::Traps are supposed to take your target down with certainty.[lr]::
54069::$$$message_0470_0001_0002$$$::If he was on guard for your attack even after you were trapped, that would mean his trap failed."::
54070::$$$message_0470_0002_0000$$$::"I see. That's such a perfectionist way of thinking."[lr]::
54071::$$$message_0470_0002_0001$$$::"It's normal for me. If you want to capture your prey alive, then there's no need to get into the same box with them."::

